{"tid":1608033,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［國際新聞］中共70年","createTime":"2019-10-01T06:54:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T07:17:55.000Z","uid":48973,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"55c5c3be3accb0731fe8ff6ec387ad8b038518eb","tid":1608033,"uid":48973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T06:54:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XLHq37V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXLHq37V.jpg&h=35c56b7f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b870a204fb7ea742279dd329c892635f478f610c","tid":1608033,"uid":48973,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T06:57:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aHU81Vh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaHU81Vh.jpg&h=10e475f0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ca97980ab805e3b79c4dd51937c8df2d73609890","tid":1608033,"uid":48973,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T06:58:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MJFcJ89.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMJFcJ89.jpg&h=b4b49b23&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6ecc0f89b485e5b2be47b42d09ff255681251697","tid":1608033,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T06:58:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14076124697f4939c36d141b0aba5adb3b310ef3","tid":1608033,"uid":69886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T06:59:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9113f82247ded2c7a88df83a567f3e145faa316","tid":1608033,"uid":169646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T06:59:49.000Z","msg":"香港國殤日 &gt;&gt;&gt; 中国国慶日 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd5ffa355388a27c00c5ebe68ac0f1ce4911fd7f","tid":1608033,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T07:00:02.000Z","msg":"<strong>我以颱風風眼橫過比喻，預測閱兵期間香港唔會發生衝突</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">昨日警察不斷恐嚇大家十一唔好出，同埋有很多假消息話各地暴徒會燒商場，呢個奇怪現象同早幾日批不反對通知書後立即大搜捕完全不同，<span style=\"color: red;\">就係因為警察知道，十一當日唔可以捉人、唔可以出現血腥畫面，</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">但中共又唔容許有大量人上街反共反雜，所以先嚇定大家。<br />\n</span><br />\n現在就好似颱風風眼即將略過時候，警察瘋狂捉人，製造白色恐怖。<span style=\"color: red;\">風眼將會在閱兵期間橫過香港，忽然晴天萬里，到時候社會上一定太平無事，警察唔會拉人，大家可以放膽出街。</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">但要小心，當10月1日半夜過後，就有可能好似風眼過後，又出現狂風暴雨，</span>所以大家意見表達完結後，就盡快返歸，唔好戀戰。<br />\n<br />\n點解警察聽日閱兵期間唔捉人？<span style=\"color: gold;\">因為北大人唔想在世界各地直播閱兵期間，同時直播出現血腥鎮壓嘅場面，咁會落佢面，令雜種即時受到黨內外以及西方社會譴責，</span>所以十一閱兵嘅時候唔會清場鎮壓。<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">聽講呢個安排僅十一閱兵嘅時段限定！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1606271\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1606271</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n今日香港慘劇係雜種一手造成，冤有頭債有主，請大家對準政權目標<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有明確訊息證實係習近平一人當日堅持拒絕「撤回」及下令將44人極速起訴暴動！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1602129\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1602129</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">十一遊行要高叫「天滅中共！習近平全家死」口號落中共面！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568634\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568634</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"221ca264ba8bbc6ac6f61b8c58a0d7e744cf1e82","tid":1608033,"uid":48973,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T07:00:22.000Z","msg":"多谢各位为中国大喜登上国际而努力"},{"pid":"25c31b29a761b91ce007199ff48ae